Question: Is the platform made of the same material as the post?

Reference Answer: yes

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/n542609.jpg

Original program:

```
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='post')
IMAGE0=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE0,object='platform')
IMAGE1=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX1)
ANSWER0=VQA(image=IMAGE0,question='What material is the post made of?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=IMAGE1,question='What material is the platform made of?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER0} == {ANSWER1} else 'no'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
